#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The man:ahci[4] driver supports AHCI compatible controllers having PCI "
#| "class 1 (mass storage), subclass 6 (SATA) and programming interface 1 "
#| "(AHCI)."
msgid ""
"The man:ahci[4] driver supports AHCI compatible controllers having PCI class "
"1 (mass storage), subclass 6 (SATA) and programming interface 1 (AHCI)."
msgstr ""
"Драйвер man:ahci[4] поддерживает AHCI-совместимые контроллеры, имеющие PCI "
"класс 1 (массовое хранилище), подкласс 6 (SATA) и программный интерфейс 1 "
"(AHCI)."

#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/15.1R/hardware.adoc:484
msgid ""
"Also, in cooperation with atamarvell and atajmicron drivers of ata(4), it "
"supports AHCI part of legacy-PATA + AHCI-SATA combined controllers, such as "
"JMicron JMB36x and Marvell 88SE61xx."
msgstr ""
"Также, в сотрудничестве с драйверами atamarvell и atajmicron из ata(4), он "
"поддерживает AHCI-часть комбинированных контроллеров legacy-PATA + AHCI-"
"SATA, таких как JMicron JMB36x и Marvell 88SE61xx."

#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/15.1R/hardware.adoc:504
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "using Intel Rapid Storage Technology (RST).  To use the nvme(4) device, "
#| "either one must set the SATA mode in the BIOS to AHCI (from RST), or one "
#| "must accept the performance with RST enabled due to interrupt sharing."
msgid ""
"The **ahci** driver also supports AHCI devices that act as PCI bridges for "
"nvme(4)  using Intel Rapid Storage Technology (RST).  To use the nvme(4)  "
"device, either one must set the SATA mode in the BIOS to AHCI (from RST), or "
"one must accept the performance with RST enabled due to interrupt sharing.  "
"FreeBSD will automatically detect AHCI devices with this extension that are "
"in RST mode.  When that happens, **ahci** will attach nvme(4)  children to "
"the **ahci** device."
msgstr ""
"с использованием Intel Rapid Storage Technology (RST). Чтобы использовать "
"устройство nvme(4), необходимо либо установить режим SATA в BIOS на AHCI "
"(вместо RST), либо смириться с производительностью при включённом RST из-за "
"разделения прерываний."

